CLS
ECHO.
ECHO -------------------------------------------------------
ECHO IF YOU HAVE UPDATED YOUR TBC-DB DATABASE MAKE SURE THAT
ECHO YOU REMEMBER TO COMPILE YOUR UPDATED CMANGOS AND SD2
